{"lastModified":1761258286106,"uri":"c::9511881484::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: British Virgin Islands / Virgin Islands, Caribbean Leewards, Caribbean Windwards\n\nWelcome Aboard Semper Fidelis – Alegria 67\n\nStep into a world of refined elegance aboard Semper Fidelis, a 2022 Fountaine Pajot Alegria 67 that sets a new standard in luxury catamaran charters. With four exquisitely appointed guest cabins—including a lavish master suite—this yacht offers a sanctuary of sophistication and comfort for up to eight guests.\n\nFrom her sleek, modern lines to the indulgent features like a private on-deck hot tub, Semper Fidelis is designed for discerning travelers seeking an elevated sailing experience. Her expansive outdoor spaces, refined interior finishes, and attentive crew create the perfect environment for unforgettable moments at sea.\n\nNow charting a course through the Caribbean’s most breathtaking destinations, Semper Fidelis is available for winter charters in the British Virgin Islands, St. Martin, and St. Barths, and summer voyages in the stunning Grenadines.\n\nWhether you're celebrating a special occasion or simply craving the ultimate escape, Semper Fidelis promises a seamless blend of adventure, relaxation, and first-class hospitality.","blueprint":{"name":"SEMPER FIDELIS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::879e0e60-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::88c0e380-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8f0d7000-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::90296750-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9fb13bd0-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100783-Oywh-aH6e.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9d9b0600-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a0d6a900-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::aaf7bd20-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::aaf747f0-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::aaf65d90-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ef986740-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ef97f210-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ef977ce0-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ef96b990-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f7ace280-a314-11ee-8659-c91f3ab76a7d.jpeg/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Fountaine Pajot","model":"Alegria 67","maxCrew":2,"sleeps":8,"cruisingCapacity":0,"builtYear":2022,"architect":"","interiorDesigner":"","topSpeed":10,"cruiseSpeed":8,"fuelCapacity":0,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Queen Cabins","value":"4"}],"cabins":4,"bathrooms":4,"length":20.43,"beam":9.75,"draft":1.8,"hullType":"","hullConstruction":"","tonnage":"","superStructure":[],"engines":"","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Jacuzzi"},{"label":"Deck Shower"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Ice Maker"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Children Allowed"}],"toys":[{"label":"Dinghy (8pax)","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Snorkel Gear","quantity":"8"},{"label":"Wake Board"},{"label":"Water Skis Adult"},{"label":"Floating Mats","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Beach Games","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Water Skis Kids"},{"label":"Swim Platform","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Fishing Gear"},{"label":"Sea Bobs"}],"entertainment":["Salon Stereo","Salon TV","Sat TV","Onboard WIFI"],"tenders":[]},"crew":[{"name":"Will Jameson","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::9511881484::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::63afdd90-989e-11f0-a1f6-1576101c0396/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Captain Will brings a wealth of experience and a passion for adventure to Semper Fidelis. With more than 15,000 nautical miles logged, he has built an impressive career across charter operations, ocean deliveries, and yacht refits, combining hands-on technical expertise with an exceptional flair for guest service.\n\nWill is a RYA Yachtmaster Offshore and is currently completing his Yachtmaster Ocean certification. His qualifications extend beyond sailing, including PADI Open Water, RYA Dinghy Instructor, and BKSA Kitesurf Instructor, which allow him to safely introduce guests to a wide range of on-the-water activities.\n\nPrior to joining Semper Fidelis, Will captained luxury crewed catamarans in the British Virgin Islands, including the Bali 5.4, where he developed a reputation for keeping yachts in impeccable condition, managing every system onboard, and curating unique itineraries that showcased the hidden gems of the Caribbean. He has also successfully delivered yachts across the Atlantic and throughout the Caribbean, demonstrating his calm leadership and skill in both offshore passages and guest-focused cruising.\n\nGuests consistently praise Will’s professionalism, warmth, and ability to create a relaxed yet adventurous atmosphere. From meticulously maintaining Semper Fidelis to leading unforgettable snorkeling, kitesurfing, and island-hopping adventures, Will ensures every charter is smooth, safe, and truly memorable.\n\nWhen he’s not at the helm, Will enjoys skiing, watersports, and photography—often capturing the magic of charter life with his FAA-certified drone skills. His dedication, technical know-how, and enthusiasm for sharing the beauty of the sea make him the perfect captain to lead your journey aboard Semper Fidelis.\n\nQualifications:\n• Yacht Master Oﬀshore CE\n• BKSA Kitesurf instructor\n• RYA Dinghy Instructor\n• RYA PB2\n• RYA Short Range Radio\n• Level 3 IMI Mechanic\n• PADI Open Water\n• DJI (FAA part 107) Drone Pilot Certification\n• Yacht Master Ocean (Exam September 2025)"},{"name":"Milou Van Melick","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::9511881484::vessel::d5cc4f30-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7da42710-989e-11f0-a1f6-1576101c0396/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Chef Milou Van Melick\n\nBorn and raised in the Netherlands, Chef Milou brings creativity, passion, and international flair to the table. With professional training in Europe and experience in both high-end restaurants and luxury yachts, she has developed a culinary style that blends Mediterranean elegance, fresh Caribbean flavors, and a focus on nutrition and balance.\n\nMilou has honed her craft across kitchens in the Netherlands, Spain, Italy, and Australia, working as a Sous Chef, Private Chef, and Farm Chef before transitioning fully into the yachting industry. Most recently, she has been the chef aboard the Bali 5.4 in the British Virgin Islands, where her inventive menus and beautifully presented dishes earned her glowing guest reviews and repeat bookings.\n\nHer background in hospitality management and event planning gives her a unique edge—she not only creates exquisite meals but also curates memorable dining experiences. Guests can expect thoughtful pairings, vibrant plating, and menus that balance indulgence with health-conscious variety. From fresh seafood feasts and refined Mediterranean classics to colorful plant-based creations, Milou thrives on tailoring each charter to her guests’ preferences.\n\nKnown for her energy, optimism, and creativity, Milou ensures that every meal aboard *Semper Fidelis* is both a delight and a lasting memory. Whether it’s a sunrise breakfast on deck, a casual beach barbecue, or a fine-dining experience under the stars, she transforms dining into one of the highlights of your yacht vacation.\n\nc e r t i f i c a t e s\nstcw + pdsd • 2024\nfood allergy awareness • 2024\nlevel 2 food safety and hygiene for catering • 2024\nculinary training | citrus food concepts | wout vereecken• 2025"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"USD","price":5600000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":5600000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"USD","price":6000000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":6000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Caribbean Low Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"USD","charterFee":5600000,"inputAmountTaxed":"INCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":5600000,"amount":5600000,"conditions":"All-Inclusive"}],"total":5600000,"subTotal":5600000,"totalTax":0},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Anguilla","type":"Dependency","category":["North America","Caribbean","Anguilla"],"coordinates":[-63.06498926535688,18.22395950228264],"bbox":[-63.16000976562499,18.17138671875,-62.97958984374999,18.269726562499997]},{"label":"Antigua and Barb.","type":"Sovereign country","category":["North America","Caribbean","Antigua and Barb."],"coordinates":[-61.93165875524458,17.253271156347328],"bbox":[-62.34826033833981,16.931